<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>VEXU STORE</title>
  <meta name="description" content="VEXU STORE - Moda premium com experiência de compra moderna e profissional." />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0b0d12;
      --bg-soft: #121722;
      --card: #151b27;
      --card-2: #1b2332;
      --line: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      --text: #f5f7fb;
      --muted: #a7b0c0;
      --primary: #4f8cff;
      --primary-2: #7aa8ff;
      --success: #2ecc71;
      --warning: #ffb84d;
      --danger: #ff6b6b;
      --shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
      --radius: 18px;
      --radius-lg: 26px;
      --max: 1240px;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: Inter, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(79,140,255,0.12), transparent 25%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(122,168,255,0.10), transparent 20%),
        var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    img {
      display: block;
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    button {
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .container {
      width: min(92%, var(--max));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #d9e4ff;
      background: rgba(79,140,255,0.14);
      border: 1px solid rgba(122,168,255,0.22);
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 86px 0;
    }

    .section-title {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: end;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .section-title h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 2.8vw, 2.8rem);
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .section-title p {
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 560px;
    }

    /* HEADER */
    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      background: rgba(11, 13, 18, 0.82);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .nav {
      min-height: 78px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .brand-mark {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #a3c2ff);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      color: white;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .nav-links {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      gap: 24px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.96rem;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: white;
    }

    .nav-actions {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 14px 20px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: 0.25s ease;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-2));
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(79,140,255,0.28);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      filter: brightness(1.05);
    }

    .btn-ghost {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      color: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .btn-ghost:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    }

    .menu-toggle {
      display: none;
      background: transparent;
      color: white;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    /* HERO */
    .hero {
      padding: 42px 0 36px;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
      gap: 24px;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .hero-main {
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(12,17,26,0.88), rgba(17,24,38,0.75)),
        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523398002811-999ca8dec234?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 30px;
      min-height: 560px;
      padding: 42px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .hero-main h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4.8rem);
      line-height: 0.98;
      margin: 18px 0 18px;
      max-width: 700px;
    }

    .hero-main p {
      max-width: 560px;
      color: #d8e0ef;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      margin-bottom: 26px;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .hero-metrics {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .metric {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .metric h3 {
      font-size: 1.45rem;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .metric p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    /* DASHBOARD CARD */
    .dashboard-card {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--card), var(--card-2));
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 30px;
      padding: 24px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .dash-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .dash-head h3 {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
    }

    .online {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #d8ffea;
      background: rgba(46,204,113,0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(46,204,113,0.25);
      padding: 8px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
    }

    .dash-stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .dash-box {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 18px;
    }

    .dash-box span {
      display: block;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .dash-box strong {
      font-size: 1.45rem;
    }

    .progress-wrap {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .progress-top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    .progress-bar {
      height: 10px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 999px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .progress-fill {
      width: 72%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary), #9dc2ff);
      border-radius: 999px;
    }

    .mini-orders {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .mini-orders h4 {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .order {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 12px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      font-size: 0.94rem;
    }

    .order:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
      padding-bottom: 0;
    }

    .order small {
      display: block;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .status {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 8px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      white-space: nowrap;
      height: fit-content;
    }

    .status.paid {
      color: #ddffea;
      background: rgba(46,204,113,0.13);
      border: 1px solid rgba(46,204,113,0.22);
    }

    .status.pending {
      color: #fff0d1;
      background: rgba(255,184,77,0.14);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,184,77,0.24);
    }

    /* BENEFITS */
    .benefits-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    .benefit {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding: 22px;
      border-radius: 20px;
    }

    .benefit h3 {
      font-size: 1.02rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .benefit p {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    /* FILTER */
    .filters {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 26px;
    }

    .filter-btn {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      color: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .filter-btn.active,
    .filter-btn:hover {
      background: rgba(79,140,255,0.16);
      border-color: rgba(122,168,255,0.35);
    }

    /* PRODUCTS */
    .products-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .product-card {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.03), rgba(255,255,255,0.025));
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 24px;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: 0.25s ease;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .product-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      border-color: rgba(122,168,255,0.26);
    }

    .product-image {
      position: relative;
      height: 290px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #0f1420;
    }

    .product-image img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      transition: 0.35s ease;
    }

    .product-card:hover .product-image img {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .tag {
      position: absolute;
      top: 14px;
      left: 14px;
      background: rgba(11,13,18,0.78);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .product-content {
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .product-category {
      color: var(--primary-2);
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .product-content h3 {
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .product-content p {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.93rem;
      min-height: 44px;
    }

    .product-bottom {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .price-box {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .price-old {
      color: #7f899a;
      text-decoration: line-through;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
    }

    .price {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .buy-btn {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-2));
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
      min-width: 112px;
    }

    .buy-btn:hover {
      filter: brightness(1.06);
    }

    /* OFFER */
    .offer-box {
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(79,140,255,0.18), rgba(13,18,29,0.84)),
        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1445205170230-053b83016050?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 42px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .offer-box h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.8vw, 3.2rem);
      line-height: 1.05;
      max-width: 650px;
      margin: 14px 0 16px;
    }

    .offer-box p {
      color: #dbe5f7;
      max-width: 580px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    /* SOCIAL PROOF */
    .proof-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .proof-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding: 22px;
      border-radius: 22px;
    }

    .proof-card p {
      color: #d7deec;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .proof-card strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .proof-card span {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    /* CTA */
    .cta-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .cta-card {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--card), var(--card-2));
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 28px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .cta-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin: 10px 0 10px;
    }

    .cta-card p {
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .cta-card ul {
      list-style: none;
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      color: #dbe2ef;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .cta-card li::before {
      content: "✓ ";
      color: var(--success);
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer {
      padding: 28px 0 50px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .footer-top {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 22px;
      padding-top: 28px;
    }

    .footer-col h4 {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .footer-col p,
    .footer-col a {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.94rem;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .footer-col a:hover {
      color: white;
    }

    .footer-bottom {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 18px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    /* CART */
    .cart-button {
      position: fixed;
      right: 22px;
      bottom: 22px;
      z-index: 1200;
      width: 64px;
      height: 64px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-2));
      color: white;
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 35px rgba(79,140,255,0.35);
    }

    .cart-count {
      position: absolute;
      top: -2px;
      right: -1px;
      min-width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #fff;
      color: #0b0d12;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      padding: 0 6px;
    }

    .cart-panel {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      right: -430px;
      width: min(100%, 420px);
      height: 100vh;
      background: #0f1420;
      border-left: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: -20px 0 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.28);
      z-index: 1300;
      transition: right 0.3s ease;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .cart-panel.open {
      right: 0;
    }

    .cart-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 22px 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .cart-items {
      flex: 1;
      overflow-y: auto;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .cart-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 74px 1fr auto;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 12px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 18px;
    }

    .cart-item img {
      width: 74px;
      height: 74px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 14px;
    }

    .cart-item h4 {
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .cart-item p {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .qty-box {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      width: fit-content;
    }

    .qty-box button {
      background: transparent;
      color: white;
      font-size: 1rem;
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
    }

    .remove-btn {
      background: transparent;
      color: #ff9b9b;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      align-self: start;
    }

    .cart-footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding: 18px 20px 20px;
      background: #0d121b;
    }

    .cart-summary {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .cart-summary div {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .cart-total {
      color: white;
      font-size: 1.12rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .empty-cart {
      color: var(--muted);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 16px;
    }

    .close-btn {
      background: transparent;
      color: white;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }

    /* WHATSAPP */
    .whatsapp {
      position: fixed;
      right: 22px;
      bottom: 96px;
      z-index: 1190;
      width: 58px;
      height: 58px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #25d366;
      color: white;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-size: 1.45rem;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(37,211,102,0.28);
    }

    /* RESPONSIVE */
    @media (max-width: 1100px) {
      .hero-grid,
      .cta-grid,
      .footer-top {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .products-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }

      .benefits-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }

      .proof-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .nav-links {
        position: absolute;
        top: 79px;
        left: 4%;
        right: 4%;
        background: #101622;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 18px;
        display: none;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .nav-links.open {
        display: flex;
      }

      .menu-toggle {
        display: block;
      }

      .nav-actions .btn-ghost {
        display: none;
      }

      .hero-main {
        padding: 28px;
        min-height: 500px;
      }

      .hero-metrics,
      .dash-stats {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .products-grid,
      .benefits-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .hero-main h1 {
        line-height: 1.02;
      }

      .offer-box,
      .cta-card,
      .dashboard-card {
        padding: 22px;
      }

      .product-image {
        height: 260px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="container nav">
      <a href="#inicio" class="brand">
        <div class="brand-mark">V</div>
        <span>VEXU STORE</span>
      </a>

      <ul class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
        <li><a href="#inicio">Início</a></li>
        <li><a href="#produtos">Produtos</a></li>
        <li><a href="#ofertas">Ofertas</a></li>
        <li><a href="#clientes">Avaliações</a></li>
        <li><a href="#contato">Contato</a></li>
      </ul>

      <div class="nav-actions">
        <a href="#produtos" class="btn btn-ghost">Ver coleção</a>
        <a href="#ofertas" class="btn btn-primary">Comprar agora</a>
        <button class="menu-toggle" id="menuToggle">☰</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="inicio" class="hero">
    <div class="container hero-grid">
      <section class="hero-main">
        <div class="badge">⚡ Loja premium com compra rápida</div>
        <h1>Moda forte. Compra simples. Visual profissional.</h1>
        <p>
          A VEXU STORE foi pensada para vender com clareza, confiança e impacto visual.
          Uma experiência moderna para quem quer comprar rápido e voltar a comprar.
